The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge offers virtual and self-guided tours as well as online leasing!
Take a tour and rent an apartment without leaving your couch.
The Timbers at Issaquah Ridge is a premier apartment community situated amongst beautiful scenery in the heart of Issaquah.
Community amenities include an upgraded resident lounge, media room, theater, playground and Wi-Fi lounge.
Our homes feature generous sized flats and townhomes with upgraded interiors, large windows that provide gorgeous mountain views and private patios or balconies.
Choose from our one-, two-, three- and four-bedroom layouts for a home that is just minutes to the Microsoft Connector and Amazon Ride bus stops.
Contact us for additional details about our preferred employer discounts!
